  "title": "Hotel Housekeeping Attendant [Dhoby Ghaut | In-house] #EC",
  "description": "<p>The client who is a hotel near to Dhoby Ghaut MRT, is looking for Housekeeping Attendant to join their team:</p><ul><li>able to work 2 rotating shifts (7am to 3pm & 3pm to 11pm)</li><li>Salary up to $2,100</li><li>AWS, performance bonus and meal/uniform provided, or meal allowance given</li></ul><p><strong>Challenges:</strong></p><p>• Maintain cleanliness of guest rooms<br />• Replenish supplies<br />• Clean lounges at guest corridor<br />• Report missing items from the room to the supervisor/Management<br />• Report damaged property to the supervisor/Management<br />• Carry out other ad hoc duties assigned by supervisor/Management</p><p><strong>What it Takes :</strong></p><p>• Minimum one year experience/ relevant experience in similar capacity<br />• Able to perform shift duties<br />• Good customer service</p><p>Interested Applicants, please submit a copy of your updated resume (in MS Word Format) and send to edan@talentsatwork.sg</p><p>Talents@Work Pte Ltd (21C0501)<br />Chin Long (Edan) - R23116697</p><p><em>*We regret to inform that only shortlisted candidate will be notified. Thank you</em></p>",
